but it was a non-working number.

00:28:53.966 --> 00:28:55.276
Did you get a new phone?

00:28:55.717 --> 00:28:57.717
Yes, it's been some time
since I changed my phone.

00:29:00.072 --> 00:29:01.907
Didn't I tell you my new number?

00:29:03.659 --> 00:29:06.078
