I'll tell you now.

00:29:07.437 --> 00:29:09.789
Oh, that's why you never texted back.

00:29:18.037 --> 00:29:19.077
I'll save it.

00:29:31.954 --> 00:29:34.606
- Use one leg only.
- You're really good.

00:29:34.689 --> 00:29:36.689
Why can't I do it naturally?

00:29:36.842 --> 00:29:38.842
- Gosh. Just my wrists?
- And turn your wrists.

00:29:39.595 --> 00:29:41.163
One and two.

00:29:41.246 --> 00:29:43.246
- One and two.
- And point.

00:29:48.036 --> 00:29:49.329
Yeon-jeong.

00:29:50.397 --> 00:29:52.541
You're doing it again.

00:29:53.275 --> 00:29:55.099
Your face when you dance.

00:29:55.183 --> 00:29:57.296
Why do you do this?

00:29:59.339 --> 00:30:01.216
That's so weird.

00:30:02.017 --> 00:30:05.479
It's so cringe.
Don't you agree, Gwang-jae?

00:30:05.562 --> 00:30:06.813
It's cringe, right?

00:30:11.777 --> 00:30:15.739
But you're supposed to smile a bit
when you're locking, so...

00:30:15.822 --> 00:30:18.066
I know that.

00:30:18.508 --> 00:30:19.692
I know.

00:30:20.135 --> 00:30:22.571
That's not what I mean.

00:30:23.263 --> 00:30:25.263
I'm saying it doesn't suit her.

00:30:25.346 --> 00:30:27.659
It's so cringeworthy.

00:30:28.577 --> 00:30:30.788
She always has that depressed look
on her face.

00:30:32.856 --> 00:30:34.299
Sorry, Yeon-jeong.

00:30:34.900 --> 00:30:37.127
I'm not trying to say that you're ugly.

00:30:37.210 --> 00:30:39.363
That's definitely not true.

00:30:40.347 --> 00:30:41.782
You don't get it.

00:30:41.865 --> 00:30:44.117
You should have seen her
when she was in high school.

00:30:44.200 --> 00:30:47.846
Her face was depressed as heck.

00:30:49.164 --> 00:30:52.292
Oh, I get it now.
You tend to do that to close friends.

00:30:52.375 --> 00:30:53.919
I know what that's like.
But you know what?

00:30:54.002 --> 00:30:56.002
From an objective point of view,
it's not weird at all.

00:30:56.085 --> 00:30:57.355
You look so cool.

00:31:01.860 --> 00:31:03.860
Yes, I'm the asshole.

00:31:06.014 --> 00:31:08.492
- Come on. Let's just drink.
- Go away.

00:31:16.984 --> 00:31:20.421
Yeon-jeong, do that little dance again.

00:31:21.305 --> 00:31:22.589
You know? Like this.

00:31:23.090 --> 00:31:24.466
Chae-yeong, you're drunk.

00:31:29.538 --> 00:31:33.225
Oh, please. Do that little dance again.
Just once.

00:31:34.768 --> 00:31:36.436
- Do it.
- Kim Chae-yeong.

00:31:38.964 --> 00:31:40.607
You're being really rude to her.

00:31:47.280 --> 00:31:48.698
I don't believe this.

00:31:49.116 --> 00:31:50.576
Why do you care?

00:31:52.936 --> 00:31:55.239
Just go home. You're being obnoxious.

00:32:04.489 --> 00:32:05.799
Moron.

00:32:06.266 --> 00:32:07.676
I wouldn't stay, even if you begged me.

00:32:08.885 --> 00:32:10.637
You're always chasing after anyone,
anyway.

00:32:10.829 --> 00:32:13.056
Did you wash your hair with beer
or something?

00:32:13.915 --> 00:32:16.559
You look freaking lame. Do you know that?

00:32:16.752 --> 00:32:19.313
- Chae-yeong.
- Don't touch me!

00:32:22.007 --> 00:32:24.609
Damn it. Don't get cocky with me.

00:32:24.692 --> 00:32:26.028
Hey, Skidmark.

00:32:27.404 --> 00:32:29.656
Did you honestly think I was your friend
just because I hung out with you?

00:32:29.739 --> 00:32:32.075
- That's enough.
- Get off me.

00:32:40.317 --> 00:32:43.337
Not once did I ever consider you a friend.

00:32:47.182 --> 00:32:49.182
Are you being serious?

00:32:50.340 --> 00:32:52.262
Get your hands off me!

00:33:04.357 --> 00:33:05.817
Get out of my face.

00:33:37.015 --> 00:33:38.266
I'm sorry.

00:33:39.768 --> 00:33:41.311
It's my fault.

00:33:43.730 --> 00:33:45.148
Does it look like

00:33:46.858 --> 00:33:48.276
I washed it with beer to you too?

00:33:48.860 --> 00:33:49.903
What?

00:33:51.071 --> 00:33:52.447
My hair, I mean.

00:33:55.075 --> 00:33:57.536
No, not at all.

00:33:58.270 --> 00:34:00.497
That's a trend in the US.

00:34:00.647 --> 00:34:02.165
I knew you'd know!

00:34:02.249 --> 00:34:05.661
Of course, I do.
Eminem also has that hair color.

00:34:05.744 --> 00:34:07.295
Tell me about it!

00:34:07.387 --> 00:34:09.047
It kept gnawing at me

00:34:09.130 --> 00:34:11.132
after she said
it looked like I washed it with beer.

00:34:11.341 --> 00:34:12.759
Seriously.

00:34:17.802 --> 00:34:19.987
It's an American style.

00:34:20.317 --> 00:34:21.851
She doesn't get it.

00:34:22.200 --> 00:34:23.744
- Hold on.
- What?

00:34:36.683 --> 00:34:38.118
That's smart.

00:34:39.369 --> 00:34:40.579
Thanks.

00:34:46.343 --> 00:34:48.837
I listened to that CD by... Was it Sisoo?

00:34:48.920 --> 00:34:50.338
It was so good.

00:34:51.422 --> 00:34:54.675
- Do you mean Sisqó?
- Yes, Sisqó.

00:34:54.759 --> 00:34:57.262
- His songs are so good, right?
- How did you know about him?

00:34:57.396 --> 00:35:00.390
- A friend from my dance club told me.
- Really?

00:35:24.214 --> 00:35:27.083
Stop moving. It's not dry yet.

00:35:52.801 --> 00:35:54.027
You have big hands.

00:36:56.740 --> 00:36:58.592
I'm telling you!

00:36:58.675 --> 00:37:02.079
Don't just be nice to us when we're here.
Answer our calls once in a while.

00:37:02.162 --> 00:37:04.398
- He's right.
- That way, I can buy some drinks here.

00:37:04.481 --> 00:37:06.333
- Or we can all go outside and drink.
- Yes.

00:37:06.417 --> 00:37:09.478
- We should drink soju outside.
- Yes, just today.

00:37:10.086 --> 00:37:12.230
Hey, what are you thinking about?

00:37:14.474 --> 00:37:17.151
- Shoot.
- Oh, my gosh.

00:37:17.302 --> 00:37:19.404
Are you all right? Are you hurt?

00:37:19.821 --> 00:37:21.030
- Go to the back.
- Gosh, what the hell?

00:37:21.114 --> 00:37:23.081
- Damn it, this hurts.
- Oh, dear.

00:37:23.616 --> 00:37:26.327
- Damn it.
- I'm terribly sorry.

00:37:27.562 --> 00:37:29.831
- Gosh.
- Let me see that.

00:37:30.215 --> 00:37:32.917
- Are you okay?
- I'm fine.

00:37:33.652 --> 00:37:35.879
She was feeling unwell today,

00:37:36.171 --> 00:37:38.171
but I made her come to work.

00:37:38.281 --> 00:37:40.975
- She should have taken a day off, then.
- I know!

00:37:41.058 --> 00:37:43.845
It's all my fault. I'm so sorry.

00:38:31.292 --> 00:38:34.153
You look amazing in a suit!

00:38:34.236 --> 00:38:36.439
It feels a bit awkward
wearing a suit again after so long.

00:38:39.042 --> 00:38:40.735
How do I look? Do you like it?

00:38:41.369 --> 00:38:42.470
I love it.

00:38:43.571 --> 00:38:44.989
This is your type, isn't it?

00:38:45.181 --> 00:38:46.241
Yes.

00:38:47.449 --> 00:38:51.246
No, I just meant
that you looked good in it.

00:38:52.455 --> 00:38:54.582
Oh, right. Let's go to this...

00:38:54.791 --> 00:38:57.085
after your interview today.

00:38:57.168 --> 00:38:58.928
LOTTE WORLD, ALL-DAY PASS

00:38:59.011 --> 00:39:00.130
Wait.

00:39:00.213 --> 00:39:01.589
You remembered?

