- What do you mean?
- What's this about?

00:39:05.101 --> 00:39:07.970
- I love you so much, Min-gi.
- What is it?

00:39:08.053 --> 00:39:10.890
I told him that I had never been
to Lotte World since high school.

00:39:12.058 --> 00:39:13.476
How attentive you are.

00:39:13.559 --> 00:39:15.812
Anyway, let's go there after
your interview.

00:39:16.771 --> 00:39:18.898
All right. I'm going to kill it.

00:39:18.981 --> 00:39:21.150
- You've got this.
- I'm running late. Bye.

00:39:21.233 --> 00:39:22.786
- You can do it!
- I can do it.

00:39:22.869 --> 00:39:24.095
- Good luck.
- You got this.

00:39:24.178 --> 00:39:25.060
I'll see you later.

00:39:27.448 --> 00:39:28.699
Why am I so nervous?

00:39:33.380 --> 00:39:34.581
Seol-ha!

00:39:35.873 --> 00:39:36.999
Yes?

00:39:37.484 --> 00:39:38.502
Good luck!

00:39:43.406 --> 00:39:44.590
I'll see you tonight.

00:39:53.124 --> 00:39:55.124
- Ms. Yun Seol-ha?
- Yes.

00:39:56.377 --> 00:39:58.813
You were a team leader at YT Company.

00:39:59.455 --> 00:40:01.758
- Yes.
- That's impressive.

00:40:01.841 --> 00:40:03.734
The head of a team at the age of 26.

00:40:04.093 --> 00:40:06.445
Yes. I had worked there as an intern...

00:40:06.528 --> 00:40:08.697
since I was a college sophomore.

00:40:10.783 --> 00:40:12.076
You must be competent.

00:40:12.477 --> 00:40:13.703
Thank you.

00:40:17.607 --> 00:40:20.168
Yeo-jin, do you need me to do
anything else before I leave?

00:40:20.251 --> 00:40:23.504
No, you've done all you could.
Thanks for today. Get ready to leave.

00:40:24.005 --> 00:40:25.465
Are you going straight to Lotte World?

00:40:25.549 --> 00:40:28.176
Yes, I'm supposed to meet her
at the front gate.

00:40:28.259 --> 00:40:29.802
She must be so excited.

00:40:30.353 --> 00:40:32.722
- Hello.
- Can I get a pancake?

00:40:32.805 --> 00:40:35.183
That will be five dollars.
I'll bring it to your table.

00:40:36.309 --> 00:40:37.685
- I'll get going.
- Bye.

00:40:39.520 --> 00:40:42.940
Wait. You can't park there.

00:40:44.884 --> 00:40:46.884
Sir, you can't park there.

