Oh, hi.

00:40:50.365 --> 00:40:51.658
I'll take that.

00:40:53.918 --> 00:40:55.918
These are Brazilian coffee beans.

00:40:56.079 --> 00:40:58.123
- You can give them to the owner.
- You were

00:40:58.648 --> 00:41:01.918
Seol-ha's supervisor
at her previous company, right?

00:41:02.351 --> 00:41:04.351
Pardon? What...

00:41:07.507 --> 00:41:08.933
Oh, right.

00:41:09.023 --> 00:41:10.760
- At the soju bar, right?
- Yes.

00:41:10.843 --> 00:41:12.512
- You were with Seol-ha.
- I was.

00:41:12.595 --> 00:41:14.222
- It's nice to see you.
- Hello.

00:41:14.397 --> 00:41:17.308
Didn't she come to work today?

00:41:17.667 --> 00:41:19.435
Oh, she's at a job interview.

00:41:19.852 --> 00:41:21.395
Oh, an interview?

00:41:22.463 --> 00:41:25.357
Do you know which company it is?

00:41:27.026 --> 00:41:29.095
It was "Brill" something.

