00:42:37.972 --> 00:42:40.433
But I said I'd handle it
with my abilities.

00:42:40.516 --> 00:42:43.294
Just get ready to pick up the tab
for being a team leader.

00:42:44.295 --> 00:42:47.648
Mika World, Lyon Croissant,
Sangpyeong Bank...

